overview: Bride-to-be Charlotte Stokely is ready to shrug off all her inhibitions and have the time of her life at her bachelorette party. This is Charlotte's last night of fun before she gets married and she's counting on enjoying EVERY minute of it. But what she DIDN'T count on was getting swept away on a wave of desire by the night's entertainment, the luscious and exotic Jade Baker.
title: The Bachelorette
